<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<title>rtorrent cheat sheet</title>
	</head>

<body bgcolor=#111111>
	<p style="color:green;font-family:monospace;font-size:10px">
		<code>
		Main View<br>
		---------------------<br>
		^q             - quit<br>
		bksp           - add torrent<br>
		->             - view download<br>
		1 - 7          - change view<br>
		^S             - start download<br>
		^D             - stop download (or remove stopped download)<br>
		^K             - close a torrent<br>
		+ / -          - change priority<br>
<br>
		Trottling<br>
		--------------------<br>
		a / s / d      - increase upload throttle by 1 / 5 / 10 KB<br>
		z / x / c      -  decrease upload throttle by 1 / 5 / 10 KB<br>
		A / S / D      - increase download throttle by 1 / 5 / 10 KB<br>
		Z / X / C      - decrease download throttle by 1 / 5 / 10 KB<br>
		<br>
		</code>
	</p>
</body>
</html>